{"tid":2341254,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[小說特急] 全民植樹","createTime":"2020-12-26T07:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T17:22:58.000Z","uid":255045,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42c4f0214023e50b53d07916cf649a861b59d875","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NS7S0qu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNS7S0qu.jpg&h=81aae3e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Ok, roll咗機未？係咪roll咗機啦？好&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎大家嚟到全民植樹嘅現場啊。自從天氣工廠式微之後，有組織就發起咗全民植樹嘅活動。今年已經嚟到第三屆啦。現場所見都有唔少參加者，大家都喺到埋頭苦幹咁將預備好嘅樹苗，埋翻落去啲土地到。我哋身邊請嚟咗三位參加者嚟接受訪問㗎。咁不如你哋介紹下自己先啦。"},{"pid":"6fe10c5bb20252e7b2dc89a73de9d52c42c651f0","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Er&mdash;&mdash;咁我先啦。我叫阿泊。<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我⋯⋯我就咁叫首領啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫我阿出得啦。"},{"pid":"0ee22fc64126bb4f7ae97b681ff01df945ec7c18","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁點解三位會嚟參加今次嘅全民植樹嘅？"},{"pid":"e90db718b276a3522e00f3f5c75fd8f454046648","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"三個人你眼望我眼。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625e74d39acb50231b63d4b44d382e813f6cd70c","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我講先啦。我叫阿泊啊BTW，驚大家唔記得咗。"},{"pid":"efa74050c7f162108188101989e62136ff317e5b","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"首領同阿出都笑咗出聲。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f56c948301e5fea43026d51d7f55ae9e875674","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實我係佢第一屆嗰陣時已經有跟開嘅，即係我都有份參加嘅。嗰陣時天氣工廠仲未爆炸啦。不過未有事都好，佢都就收皮㗎啦。咁嗰陣時，佢嘅分支就攪咗第一次嘅全民植樹啦。咁大家都知咩原因攪㗎啦&mdash;&mdash;"},{"pid":"57b9a97349a9eaf13b44cbd2f4f0c67e01a27e67","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"阿泊望望首領同阿出。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca73c8833e84dc2a6de1a58ab438ff525aabc7f","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔知喎。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 係囉&mdash;你講吓囉。你做緊訪問啊嘛。"},{"pid":"0a5cbc7c0a95a1bbe61070690afcce637418e3cf","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"首領笑咗笑。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdd707e99ca44d0c46930a3826979ba2bcbde4c","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 咁其實就係因為嗰個分支就係一間細嘅、你當係分流商咁嘅嘢啦。咁有個阿姐就覺得依到已經無晒啲種得起嘅樹啦。明明喺8、90年代嗰陣，我哋依到種到好多五花八門、各具特色嘅大樹，仲要有好多可以紅到去日本，甚至係荷里活，即係去到國際知名嗰個level啦。係嗰陣時，天氣工廠越做越大，亦好多人入行。"},{"pid":"8959ba9c771b71c63a974ce85aa587231455a55e","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwGsPnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwGsPnf.jpg&h=b26bb815&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab176c469dcb765294fd80bf97f7c41376927390","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 但唔知點解過咗2000年打後，成件事就開始收皮。天氣工廠本身係打造一啲合適嘅氣候去培育樹，同時亦依靠樹去壯大自己嘅。但2000打後種出嚟嘅樹慢慢咁失去咗吸引支持者嘅力量。甚至乎去到之前嗰幾年&mdash;&mdash;其實依家都係咁啦&mdash;&mdash;啲人寧願睇人哋外國嘅樹，吹捧韓國嘅樹，追台灣自身獨立成長嘅樹，都唔睇本地嘅樹。咁所以嗰個阿姐本身就打著要捧翻起我哋依個地頭嘅樹，先至會舉辦依個活動嘅。咁依個就係我第一屆get到嘅message啦。"},{"pid":"50919cd1296c651701c43c3de8b2e69700e3c113","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你係有跟足三屆嘅？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 我淨係有跟第一屆，同埋今屆囉。"},{"pid":"fa39d22565779537158be6cfbc2b9812eb6c574c","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你哋呢？"},{"pid":"ba34b89727fd42c867db6abf357d5775e291724c","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"首領同阿出都搖搖頭。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff5f2dc455236463315d01d4038e939debc052e","tid":2341254,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj